    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Вояга етмаган болани чет элга кузатиб бориш ва олиб келиш тўғрисида мажбуриятнома</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#29}Ариза киритилаётган ташкилот номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Аризачининг уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#7}Аризачининг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#8}Аризачига паспорт берган ИИБ номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#9}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"a\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">М<span class=\"leading\"></span>А Ж Б У Р И Я Т Н О М А</span></p>\n<p class=\"a\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#25}Мажбуриятнома тасдиқланган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Мажбуриятнома тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> вояга етмаган фарзандим – </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#27} Аризачининг фарзанди туғилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Фарзандининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> (туғилганлик ҳақида гувоҳнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Берилган гувоҳноманинг серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Гувоҳнома берган ФХДЁ бўлими манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ФҲДЁ бўлими томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Гувоҳнома берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган) ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17} Аризачининг иккинчи фарзанди туғилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Фарзандининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ни (туғилганлик ҳақида гувоҳнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Берилган гувоҳноманинг серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Гувоҳнома берган ФХДЁ бўлимининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ФҲДЁ бўлими томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Гувоҳнома берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган) </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Аризачи ўзининг фарзандларини олиб кетадиган давлатнинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">кузатиб олиб бориш ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#28}Фарзандларини яна ортга қайтариб олиб келадиган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га қайта олиб келиш мажбуриятини ўз зиммамга оламан.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Кейинчалик ҳеч қандай моддий ва мулкий даъво қилмайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ушбу мажбуриятноманинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризачи:__________________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви. </span></p>\n</div></div>",
